    "The methods used in this research primarily focus on lexical features such as word frequency and collocations to compare and analyse these academic essays.",
    "Due to the lack of sentence-level comparison methods, the study may not fully assess the nuances of writing quality, coherence, and argumentation structure.",
    "These limitations need to be addressed in future More human than human?",
    "research to provide a more detailed and comprehensive understanding of the capabilities and limitations of AI-generated academic content compared to human writing.",
